$ Redirection with HTML

code {
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh"
        content="0;
        url=http://renenyffenegger.ch/notes/develeopment/web/HTML/redirection" />
</head></html>
code }

The value of paramenter content specifies the amount of secunds until the redirection takes place. 0 = immediatly.

